{
  "texts": [
    "Base was assessed in terms of MAP and MRR@10 values on the TREC CAR dataset.",
    "Based on the experimental results, ColBERT achieves better performance than BERT (Rep).ColBERT [104] was further improved by Lin et al. [50] by using knowledge distillation.",
    "Reimers and Gurevych introduced Sentence-BERT [86] for passage ranking to obtain sentence embeddings via the Siamese network.",
    "Similar to CEDR [112] and PARADE Avg, RepBERT [58] executes average pooling for all tokens in a passage to produce its final representation.",
    "DPR [124] trains the query encoder and the document encoder on natural questions, Triviaqa (Trivia), web questions (WQ), CuratedTrec (TREC), and Squad V1.1."
  ]
}